snippet.title: [EARLY ACCESS] Suicide For Him - Official Cast Trailer
snippet.description:
Suicide For Him is now available in Early Access on Steam!
Discover our amazing cast that voice acted our characters.

Get the game on #Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1062550

-

✅ Follow our amazing voice actors:

Kirsten Candelore - Jinkles
https://twitter.com/lovejinkles

Roberto Benavides - TheBurningFaith
https://twitter.com/BurningFaithVA

Uche Natalie Emihian - GeekyVoiceActs
https://twitter.com/GeekyVa

Paul Melendez - BodegaBelmont
https://twitter.com/AkiSmash

-

✅ Follow us!

https://starbitlight.com/
